<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Seminary Feedback</title>
    <style>
        /* General Styles */
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background-color: #f7f9fc;
            color: #333;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            min-height: 100vh;
        }

        h1, h2 {
            font-weight: 600;
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            color: #444;
        }

        form {
            background-color: #fff;
            max-width: 600px;
            padding: 30px;
            margin: 20px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }

        label {
            font-size: 16px;
            font-weight: 500;
            display: block;
            margin: 15px 0 5px;
        }

        input[type="radio"] {
            margin-right: 10px;
        }

        .scale-container {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            margin: 10px 0 20px;
        }

        .scale-container label {
            font-size: 14px;
            font-weight: normal;
        }

        textarea {
            width: 100%;
            height: 100px;
            padding: 10px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            border: 1px solid #ccc;
            border-radius: 4px;
            font-size: 14px;
            resize: none;
        }

        button {
            background-color: #007BFF;
            color: #fff;
            font-size: 16px;
            font-weight: 600;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 4px;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: background-color 0.3s;
        }

        button:hover {
            background-color: #0056b3;
        }

        .divider {
            border-top: 1px solid #ddd;
            margin: 30px 0;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <form action="/submit-feedback" method="POST">
        <h1>Seminary Feedback</h1>

        <!-- Scale Questions -->
        <h2>On a scale of 1 â€“ 5, how much did you feel like:</h2>
        
        <div>
            <label>Your relationship increased with Jesus Christ:</label>
            <div class="scale-container">
                <% for (let i = 1; i <= 5; i++) { %>
                    <label>
                        <input type="radio" name="relationshipWithChrist" value="<%= i %>" required> <%= i %>
                    </label>
                <% } %>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div>
            <label>You enjoyed coming to seminary:</label>
            <div class="scale-container">
                <% for (let i = 1; i <= 5; i++) { %>
                    <label>
                        <input type="radio" name="enjoyedSeminary" value="<%= i %>" required> <%= i %>
                    </label>
                <% } %>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div>
            <label>You gained greater understanding of the scriptures:</label>
            <div class="scale-container">
                <% for (let i = 1; i <= 5; i++) { %>
                    <label>
                        <input type="radio" name="understandingScriptures" value="<%= i %>" required> <%= i %>
                    </label>
                <% } %>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div>
            <label>Your testimony improved:</label>
            <div class="scale-container">
                <% for (let i = 1; i <= 5; i++) { %>
                    <label>
                        <input type="radio" name="testimonyImproved" value="<%= i %>" required> <%= i %>
                    </label>
                <% } %>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Divider -->
        <div class="divider"></div>

        <!-- Text Input Questions -->
        <h2>Reflection Questions</h2>

        <div>
            <label>If you had to pick 3 words to describe your experience in seminary, what would they be?</label>
            <textarea name="threeWords" required></textarea>
        </div>

        <div>
            <label>If you had to summarize one of your main takeaways in seminary this semester, what would it be?</label>
            <textarea name="mainTakeaway" required></textarea>
        </div>

        <div>
            <label>Is there any moment in seminary that will stick out in your mind for years to come?</label>
            <textarea name="memorableMoment" required></textarea>
        </div>

        <div>
            <label>Is there any specific lesson that was more meaningful to you this semester?</label>
            <textarea name="meaningfulLesson" required></textarea>
        </div>

        <div>
            <label>Is there any specific principle that you learned that was meaningful this semester?</label>
            <textarea name="meaningfulPrinciple" required></textarea>
        </div>

        <div>
            <label>What was your overall highlight of this semester of seminary?</label>
            <textarea name="semesterHighlight" required></textarea>
        </div>

        <div>
            <label>In five years from now, if you look back on this semester of seminary what will you remember?</label>
            <textarea name="fiveYearsReflection" required></textarea>
        </div>

        <button type="submit">Submit Feedback</button>
    </form>
</body>
</html>
